# @10k24/p5b

Render p5.js sketches to RGBA pixel buffers in Node.js.

NOTE: several features are untested or unsupported, including the following:
- p5.js v2.x
- webgl
- shaders
- video
- sound
- third party plugins or extensions

## Installation

```bash
npm install @10k24/p5b
```

